WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:37.619
Hey, good morning family. I have a word for you all here. Well, basically, I just wanted to do some highlights of some of the words that the Lord has given me because last night whenever I was praying about things—and just about the word that I gave yesterday and how heavy it was and what the Lord had showed me—first of all, I want to say this: I have gotten a lot of trolls on this video saying that I copied a man of God's word and brought it on here and that I was saying everything that he was saying.

00:00:37.620 --> 00:01:04.057
John Paul Jackson is his name. I said right before I quoted this, I was given a video from one of my YouTube family, one of the people on here; they sent me an email and they said, 'Look, this is something you could tell the people about all the needs that they're going to need and what they need to have,'and everything.

00:01:04.058 --> 00:01:15.118
Because I was praying about this already and I was asking the Lord, 'What do you want me to tell the people?'because everybody's needs are different throughout the world.

00:01:15.119 --> 00:01:28.080
I have listeners from everywhere; I mean literally, I look at where they're at, and I have thousands of people in Africa, thousands of people in Europe, in Asia, and everywhere.

00:01:28.081 --> 00:02:03.807
So it's different for everybody, so I'm praying and I'm seeking the Lord, and then I have a sister in the Lord give me the video and say, 'Hey, look right here, you could tell them, and this part of the video, watch this right here, and you can maybe tell your listeners how to prepare for what's coming.'So I was excited about it, so I brought those four things he said of what's true needs and all that, and people did not hear me say it, obviously, or they did hear me say it and they just want to be a troll.

00:02:03.808 --> 00:02:13.026
I don't know, I'm trying to figure it out. It's right there; I can even put the timestamp of when I said it. This was given to me and I'm trying to help you.

00:02:13.027 --> 00:02:26.191
I wasn't saying this whole prophetic word was from John Paul Jackson; that was from the Lord, and bottom line is, it distracts from what God is trying to help you all with.

00:02:26.192 --> 00:02:40.203
I know the people are reading the comments and they're making stuff up on there and they're being that way, and I hate to even bring this up, but I'm really concerned where everybody's at in the body of Christ.

00:02:40.204 --> 00:02:47.615
There's so many people that are distracted by some of the dumbest stuff.

00:02:47.616 --> 00:02:54.684
Where we are going, I don't want to—like I said, I'm not wanting to be a fearmonger. I'm not wanting to scare people.

00:02:54.685 --> 00:03:03.863
I told you all in that video that I saw people in white suits that were covered in a glory that looked like honey.

00:03:03.864 --> 00:03:08.171
It was not honey; I'm not telling you to go buy honey and eat honey.

00:03:08.172 --> 00:03:14.140
People are saying, 'Okay, I'm going to go buy a lot of honey and eat honey.'No, do not go buy honey and eat honey.

00:03:14.141 --> 00:03:17.715
The honey is a representation of what I'm trying to explain.

00:03:17.716 --> 00:03:25.387
I'm trying to talk to you and tell you about what the glory looks like in the spirit realm; it looked like honey.

00:03:25.388 --> 00:03:29.303
It's a type and shadow. Do not go buy honey and eat a lot of honey.

00:03:29.304 --> 00:03:35.072
I did not say that was going to protect you with this virus or this plague that's coming.

00:03:35.073 --> 00:03:41.113
It may, I don't know, maybe that was the type and shadow. I have no idea. It sounds foolish; that's what I'm trying to tell you.

00:03:41.114 --> 00:03:52.499
I'm not trying to pick at anybody either, I'm just trying to tell you all when I'm trying to describe something out of the spirit of what the Lord is showing me, it looked like honey.

00:03:52.500 --> 00:04:17.754
The glory of the Lord was radiating out of that human body that the Lord showed me, and it was going out about three feet, just like it talks about in the Bible that they would go and line up people down the alleyways and stuff, that even the shadow of Peter would touch them and they would be healed.

00:04:17.755 --> 00:04:42.418
That was the anointing of the Holy Ghost; it was so thick and so strong in those believers, the disciples, that the power of God—the energy of the Holy Ghost—was that much in them that it was coming out of them, that it was even the width of the shadow and it was touching the people that were sick and they were being healed by the power of God.

00:04:42.419 --> 00:04:49.524
And so the Lord was showing me that same kind of a manifestation of His glory for what's coming.

00:04:49.525 --> 00:04:59.898
'If ye abide in Me, and My words abide in you, ye shall ask what ye will, and it shall be done.'That kind of power is because we're abiding in Him.

00:04:59.899 --> 00:05:06.071
His words are going to be about Him, as I have told you in the last video; you need to get the foundation of the word inside of you.

00:05:06.072 --> 00:05:11.090
You need to get that so deep inside of you for what's coming. It is not about fear.

00:05:11.091 --> 00:05:28.495
When I told you about probably ten videos back, the Lord said there's a great storm coming, and I told you about this great storm and I told you all about the wall, and I told you that Psalm 91 and Psalm 23 would be what saves you in the storm that's coming.

00:05:28.496 --> 00:05:39.675
Every word that I have given has kind of piggybacked on the other word, and they are all like a big puzzle.

00:05:39.676 --> 00:05:59.598
So when He told you in that word—go back and look at 'The Great Storm Coming,'it has about a hundred thousand views on there; it'll really bless you—I told you that Psalm 91 and Psalm 23 are going to be your wall for this storm.

00:05:59.599 --> 00:06:05.195
You will have to know the word of God for what's coming or you're not going to make it.

00:06:05.196 --> 00:06:16.954
I talked to you about the 350 million worldwide, and people are saying, 'Well, there's only 350 million people in the United States, that's everybody.'No, please listen to me, please.

00:06:16.955 --> 00:06:24.564
This is not about the United States only; this is about waking up the church.

00:06:24.565 --> 00:06:29.324
This is about a shaking of the world. This is about Jesus Christ coming back.

00:06:29.325 --> 00:06:44.579
And then people say, 'Is this something that's happening before the Rapture or after the Rapture?'Y'all, whenever I went into the tribulation vision, I did not see a lot; I was shown a lot about the Christians that were left because they were living in compromise.

00:06:44.580 --> 00:06:55.628
They were living in a state of sin; they believed in salvation but they went back to the trash they thought they were being saved from.

00:06:55.629 --> 00:07:05.515
You cannot live a Christian life that you say you're living and live like the devil. You live like Jesus; you don't live like the devil.

00:07:05.516 --> 00:07:14.836
And so when you're trying to say, 'Well, I'm a Christian,'is there any separation from you?

00:07:14.837 --> 00:07:22.061
If you were to be in a lineup to say that person's a Christian and that person's the world, we are to be the salt; we're to stand out.

00:07:22.062 --> 00:07:30.875
And if you're not standing out, you're not going. Ten virgins: five had their lamps full of the oil, five did not.

00:07:30.876 --> 00:07:45.283
The ones that do not have the oil filled in their lamps, I believe because of the parable that Jesus gave us and the explanation, are the ones that will be left.

00:07:45.284 --> 00:08:00.850
If you are not filled with and controlled by the Holy Ghost in your life and you are praying and seeking Him on a daily basis—not just on Sunday—if you are not having a relationship with Him, this is where I'm at, this is where the Bible's at.

00:08:00.851 --> 00:08:08.914
I'm telling you this is what Jesus said: 'You prophesied in My name, you've done all these things in My name, but depart from Me, I never knew you.'He told us this.

00:08:08.915 --> 00:08:20.339
Then it even talks about it in Ephesians, it talks about this in Romans, it talks about it there in Acts; it talks about it in so many different places that the people were living in sin.

00:08:20.340 --> 00:08:28.138
The Apostle Paul was addressing the church; he was talking to the church about living in sin.

00:08:28.139 --> 00:08:38.819
If you're in adultery, if you're in fornication, if you're practicing all these things in sin, you will not be able to inherit the kingdom of God.

00:08:38.820 --> 00:08:44.338
An inheritance is something that you receive after you die.

00:08:44.339 --> 00:08:53.099
So if you're not able to receive it, he's not talking—you don't receive an inheritance if you're not part of the kingdom.

00:08:53.100 --> 00:08:57.466
You need to be a born-again believer to receive an inheritance.

00:08:57.467 --> 00:09:05.690
You have to enter into the kingdom of God, and then when you're in the kingdom of God, you have to inherit the kingdom of God.

00:09:05.691 --> 00:09:21.169
An inheritance is for the believer. The Apostle Paul was talking to the church: not living in adultery, not living in all these things.

00:09:21.170 --> 00:09:29.759
He had a huge list and he addressed each church, and he talked about it in Ephesians, he talked about it over and over and over again in the word.

00:09:29.760 --> 00:09:40.753
So he's trying to warn the believer: you cannot live in these things and think that grace alone is saving you and you can live like the world.

00:09:40.754 --> 00:09:47.561
You have to be separated and be holy unto Him. Yeah, we mess up; and I'm going to tell you this: yes, we mess up.

00:09:47.562 --> 00:09:55.643
You know, I may drop a bad word every once in a while, I might get mad, stub my toe, or say something stupid, and you do, and that's just flesh sometimes.

00:09:55.644 --> 00:09:58.362
You know what? Out of the abundance of the heart, the mouth speaks.

00:09:58.363 --> 00:10:06.251
We're all a work in progress, but I'm talking about somebody who is deliberately living what He said not to do.

00:10:06.252 --> 00:10:18.898
It's not somebody who's going, 'Man, I don't want to live this way.'But sometimes my flesh is weak, and I have a bad day and I repent. I don't run from God when I sin; I run to God when I sin.

00:10:18.899 --> 00:10:30.958
But some of these people think, 'I can live this way and make it a lifestyle, live a lifestyle of compromise, live a lifestyle of sin, and I'm still going to make the Rapture.'You are mistaken.

00:10:30.959 --> 00:10:43.132
I have seen literally tens of thousands when I went to tribulation with Jesus that were left here thinking that they were okay and their lamps were full and everything was okay and great.

00:10:43.133 --> 00:10:53.225
The Rapture is not salvation; many that are saved will not make the Rapture if they're not living in a godly state.

00:10:53.226 --> 00:11:02.320
You all kind of think, 'Well, it's just entitled to me because I said a sinner's prayer.'No, it's working out your salvation with fear and trembling.

00:11:02.321 --> 00:11:12.590
You need to know that you have to be holy as Jesus is holy, practicing a holy lifestyle.

00:11:12.591 --> 00:11:20.453
It's not living like the world and thinking, 'Well, I'm qualified; I'm sealed unto the day of redemption,'like I heard one person say.

00:11:20.454 --> 00:11:25.912
No, you're sealed by the power of the Lord if you're practicing a godly lifestyle.

00:11:25.913 --> 00:11:30.552
You're not living like hell and thinking, 'Well, I'm a Christian.'No.

00:11:30.553 --> 00:11:34.716
If you can't tell any difference between you and Jay-Z, you have a problem.

00:11:34.717 --> 00:11:58.482
If you can't tell a difference between you and some of these rap people living like the world and you go, 'Well, you know, my life is no different than theirs; I just say I'm a Jesus lover; I love the Lord.'No, we have got to separate ourselves and we've got to be like Jesus, practice what He says to do in the Bible, and be a godly influence.

00:11:58.483 --> 00:12:10.076
You say, 'Well, I'll never be able to match up to Jesus.'No, but you're trying; you keep your heart right before Him and you're seeking Him and you say, 'Jesus, I love you; I want to be more like you.

00:12:10.077 --> 00:12:19.113
I don't want to be more like the hip-hop stars; I want to be more like Jesus.'In that, I'm a work in progress; I'm being renewed.

00:12:19.114 --> 00:12:34.230
I'm working out my salvation, I'm doing all this, and I'm seeking you, Father, and I know that in the process of life, I'm becoming more like you, but I don't want to be more like the world.

00:12:34.231 --> 00:12:43.434
So that was another thing. Does this happen before or after the Rapture?

00:12:43.435 --> 00:12:52.679
I believe we are going to see a great shaking before the Rapture of the church.

00:12:52.680 --> 00:12:58.106
That will be the refiner's fire—that's a video or two back—a refiner's fire, a great thing.

00:12:58.107 --> 00:13:07.559
And this is what I told everybody: I didn't see the plague two or three days ago like I do now.

00:13:07.560 --> 00:13:14.879
The Lord showed me; He said people will say around the world that there has been a great Ichabod.

00:13:14.880 --> 00:13:25.718
If you look at that word, I didn't understand what that meant until a lot of people brought it up and I started studying it out. It's like I told you: He's going to be silent in a test.

00:13:25.719 --> 00:13:44.192
During this thing that we're about to see through finances, through all these things, the Lord showed me it will feel like you've been abandoned, but there is a glorious remnant that will rise up in this refiner's fire and lay hands on the sick.

00:13:44.193 --> 00:13:56.338
And they will cover... this is another thing that I just felt in my spirit: we are wanting to populate heaven and we're wanting to depopulate hell.

00:13:56.339 --> 00:14:03.763
If Jesus Christ was to come right now as we speak, a lot of people would go to hell.

00:14:03.764 --> 00:14:14.457
But people are like, 'Well, He's coming back in September, this month, any day now.'No, I hate to say this—I'm telling you I expect Him anytime—I just want to tell you I believe Jesus could come back at any time.

00:14:14.458 --> 00:14:22.815
But if He does right now, a lot of people are going to hell. I personally believe we have some more time.

00:14:22.816 --> 00:14:28.614
I believe it will be on the Shemitah cycles, and a lot of people don't understand that.

00:14:28.615 --> 00:14:38.851
If you go read Rabbi Jonathan Cahn's books and listen to what he says about the Shemitah cycles and about the seven-year cycles—we entered into a seven-year cycle.

00:14:38.852 --> 00:14:43.018
Some people say we entered into the tribulation already; no, we have not.

00:14:43.019 --> 00:14:50.638
Tribulation is hell on earth; it has not started yet. I'm telling you, you're missing it.

00:14:50.639 --> 00:14:55.799
I believe we will go through some stuff called the birthing pains.

00:14:55.800 --> 00:15:10.679
Whenever I told you Isaiah 60:1, 'Arise, shine, for thy light is come, and the glory of the Lord has risen upon us,'for there is great darkness on the earth and gross darkness will cover the people.

00:15:10.680 --> 00:15:15.539
It's because I told you there's compromise. This is what's happening.

00:15:15.540 --> 00:15:20.907
There's a compromise that's entered into the American culture and the churches worldwide.

00:15:20.908 --> 00:15:33.452
In Australia, wherever, there is a compromise being preached in the pulpit, and when you do not preach holiness and you don't preach repentance, it affects the morals of the nation.

00:15:33.453 --> 00:15:50.650
It affects the people and it starts trickling down; it starts at the head of the church first, and then the church teaches the family and the unit, and then there becomes a holiness and a purity inside of the church, and then it affects the nation.

00:15:50.651 --> 00:15:56.224
Then we're all upset about the politics of America, and they're like, 'Well, why is America going this way?

00:15:56.225 --> 00:16:02.257
Why do we have all this craziness going on?'Because the church is the leader of everything.

