God put us to be the salt of the earth, and when the church isn't doing right, it starts affecting the morals of the nation.

00:16:09.284 --> 00:16:14.961
Look what happened: we took prayer out of schools, then people started getting crazy in schools.

00:16:14.962 --> 00:16:27.215
When you start taking the Ten Commandments off things, you start taking off loving the Lord thy God with all your heart, mind, soul, and strength and love your neighbor as yourself and you operate in those commandments, look at what happens.

00:16:27.216 --> 00:16:35.635
Literally, the decay of the culture of the world starts to happen all around us because you become a godless people.

00:16:35.636 --> 00:16:45.381
You have to have Christ centered in your marriage, Christ centered in your home, and He has to be the cornerstone of your house.

00:16:45.382 --> 00:16:52.885
He has to be the foundation of everything you believe so that you have a godly marriage, a godly lifestyle, and godly children growing up.

00:16:52.886 --> 00:17:11.698
And as the decay of the culture of America happens—because we've replaced the Bible with what was MTV back then, with YouTube videos, and with Taylor Swift and all these people, the Kardashians—you're replacing the Bible with these people and you're feeding on that more than you're feeding on the word.

00:17:11.699 --> 00:17:19.583
