00:17:19.584 --> 00:17:29.639
So the decay of the culture of America has happened; the decay of the culture of the world, Europe, everything, and it's become a godless people.

00:17:29.640 --> 00:17:41.742
So what I'm trying to tell you is, in that process, we're going to see a great shaking, and I really believe this with all my heart.

00:17:41.743 --> 00:17:50.087
The people who are awake right now will prepare. I got persecuted for trying to help people on how to prepare, and people get all upset.

00:17:50.088 --> 00:17:55.092
Like I said, I get all kinds of crazy emails. People have some problems.

