00:19:24.573 --> 00:19:30.227
Go and do this; I have you on assignment. Do you know what I'm saying? I am not saying I am those men.

00:19:30.228 --> 00:19:44.480
I don't even feel like I'm worthy to even tie their shoes, but I'm telling you in my heart, those assignments that they had will start being spread to other prophetic voices to warn the people that this is what's coming.

00:19:44.481 --> 00:19:55.237
If the word sounds similar, it's because it's the same vein and the same anointing being distributed to His prophetic voices because they did not get to finish their race.

00:19:55.238 --> 00:20:06.488
It was a casualty of war. Does that make sense to you all? So God brings up new people to finish the war before His coming. It doesn't end; the gift doesn't die.

00:20:06.489 --> 00:20:14.077
It doesn't say, 'Well, it's over, sorry, it was a casualty of war.'No, He raises up another general like He would do in World War II or World War I or whatever.

00:20:14.078 --> 00:20:22.943
