00:20:22.944 --> 00:20:35.759
That's why when you hear other prophetic voices—because you try to compare me to other people—they sound similar because the heartbeat of the Spirit is the same.

00:20:35.760 --> 00:20:38.506
There's no difference in time; there's no difference in season.

00:20:38.507 --> 00:20:44.858
