00:21:57.111 --> 00:22:05.501
Women, like women of the night, were trying to get the Christian men, and I was like, 'This is like Sodom and Gomorrah over here.

00:22:05.502 --> 00:22:09.161
I gotta stop this.'So I'm turning off that and I'm starting my own private thing.

00:22:09.162 --> 00:22:14.314
I'm only allowed 5,000 people on that Facebook platform, so once it's full, it's full.

00:22:14.315 --> 00:22:23.812
I'm sorry, I just cannot allow the wolves to come in and try to tempt the men of God and try to mess with my people. I feel responsible for that kind of stuff.

00:22:23.813 --> 00:22:29.752
When I'm not there and I look at the comment section, I see they're having private conversations, and I'm going, 'Oh dear God, this is not good.

00:22:29.753 --> 00:22:47.968
