00:22:47.969 --> 00:23:00.605
If you do not have a picture on your name, if you do not have some kind of face and it's just a blank thing where I can't see who you are and it doesn't show a description of who you are, I'm not going to let you in.

00:23:00.606 --> 00:23:15.688
