00:23:26.826 --> 00:23:43.457
Jesus is coming, and you need to know how to stand by faith, how to pray in the Holy Ghost, and how to do the fundamentals that every believer should be doing already, to encourage you to do this because if you do not do these fundamentals, you are in trouble.

00:23:43.458 --> 00:23:56.223
