He showed me about the Great Wall—the wall of protection. He showed me about the Ichabod.

00:25:02.796 --> 00:25:09.178
He showed me about the python coming up out of the water trying to wrap around the United States with the great earthquake.

00:25:09.179 --> 00:25:23.787
If we divide Jerusalem and we see a two-state solution come to pass, know that within a couple of days—probably three days after the two-state solution has taken place—we will see this major earthquake.

00:25:23.788 --> 00:25:29.856
I've seen the dollar crash. I saw a new digital platform coming.

00:25:29.857 --> 00:25:34.321
I saw food lines. I saw cobwebs in the corners of the shelves.

00:25:34.322 --> 00:25:47.219
After you see all those things that I've told you when you look at each individual video of the warnings the Lord has told me, hopefully, this will help you put a picture together of where we are.

00:25:47.220 --> 00:25:53.280
So I hope this blesses you all, and thank you for watching. If you're still watching, God bless you guys.

00:25:53.281 --> 00:25:58.889
I'm going to pray for you right now. Father, I just thank You, Lord, for my family here.

00:25:58.890 --> 00:26:17.904
I just believe, Father, for clarity, for wisdom, and for their thoughts to be clear, that their minds are focused on You, knowing who they are in Christ, knowing that they don't have to be tormented by fear or by demonic spirits.

00:26:17.905 --> 00:26:29.158
We have authority over the devil in this earth. Father, You've given us power and authority to tread on all serpents and scorpions, and nothing shall by any means hurt us.

00:26:29.159 --> 00:26:38.388
You gave us Psalm 91; You gave us Psalm 23; You gave us these beautiful passages of scripture that we can live by.

00:26:38.389 --> 00:26:48.492
I thank You, Father, that we rise up and we are the salt of the earth, that we separate ourselves, that we're not cold and we're not lukewarm, but we are hot for You.

00:26:48.493 --> 00:27:05.810
I thank You, Father, that You are delivering us from a lukewarm spirit, that we become hot for Jesus, because in being passionate and having a relationship with You, there is great divine protection in these last days.

00:27:05.811 --> 00:27:12.239
Being lukewarm, You said You spew us out of Your mouth; being cold, You don't even recognize us.

00:27:12.240 --> 00:27:19.141
But Father, I thank You, Lord, that we are not cold and we're not lukewarm, but we are hot for Jesus.

00:27:19.142 --> 00:27:27.832
I just thank You, Lord; give us revelation knowledge. We will flow freely, uninterrupted and unhindered by any satanic or demonic force.

00:27:27.833 --> 00:27:43.777
I thank You, Lord, that You speak to our spirits and our minds, and our minds are renewed by the word of God.

00:27:43.778 --> 00:27:46.857
We hear Your voice, and a stranger's voice we will not follow.

00:27:46.858 --> 00:27:50.745
We thank You, Lord, that You speak through us. We are the salt of the earth.

00:27:50.746 --> 00:28:01.918
We are that place where we go into the places of the earth—the grocery stores, the gas stations, whatever—and we show the love of God to people.

00:28:01.919 --> 00:28:23.115
When they see us, they say, 'There's something different about you.'Just like whenever I pray for my dogs and people say, 'There's something different about your puppies; there's an anointing on your dogs.'They don't know it's an anointing, but there's a presence on your dogs.

00:28:23.116 --> 00:28:35.878
They get peace from the Holy Ghost being imparted. You impart peace into Your children; impart the presence of the Lord into your everyday life and into your business.

00:28:35.879 --> 00:28:47.050
Walk with Him, abide in Him, and He will abide in you. Thank You, Lord, for the manifestations of the presence of God in these last days.

00:28:47.051 --> 00:28:51.229
Thank You, Lord, that that glorious outpouring is coming on Your remnant.

00:28:51.230 --> 00:28:57.612
Thank You, Lord, that there is a heavenly glow around and about us like honey.

00:28:57.613 --> 00:29:07.678
Father, there is no devil in hell that can penetrate the power of God. Christ in us, the hope of glory.

00:29:07.679 --> 00:29:15.191
In You, Father, we can do exploits; we can do great and mighty things because of You, Father.

00:29:15.192 --> 00:29:25.952
I thank You, Lord, there is none of us and all of You in us. Christ in us, the hope of glory.

00:29:25.953 --> 00:29:34.565
We have this treasure in earthen vessels, that the excellency of the power will be known of You in these last days and not of us, Father.

00:29:34.566 --> 00:29:45.143
I thank You, Lord, that it'll be all about You. It'll be everything about Jesus and what He's done for us, that we're not walking in fear about a plague.

00:29:45.144 --> 00:29:51.626
Father, we thank You, Lord, for Psalm 91. We thank You, Lord, for Your blessing of Psalm 91, and we memorize that.

00:29:51.627 --> 00:29:56.785
We get it down inside of us so that no plague comes nigh. Thank You, Father.

00:29:56.786 --> 00:30:02.187
We give You all the glory and all the honor and all the praise.

00:30:02.188 --> 00:30:11.377
We rise up and grow up spiritually, and we feed on the meat of the word that it makes us strong.

00:30:11.378 --> 00:30:25.671
We're not on the milk like a baby; we grow up and go from glory to glory. Thank You, Lord. Thank You, Jesus, for Your blood.

00:30:25.672 --> 00:30:30.123
Thank You, Lord, for Your presence and Your blood that covered us from all our sins.

00:30:30.124 --> 00:30:35.424
We make much of the blood today. Thank You for the blood that covers us. Thank You, Lord, for Your covering.

00:30:35.425 --> 00:30:40.870
Lord, we give You honor and glory and praise in the mighty name of Jesus.

00:30:40.871 --> 00:30:45.506
And everybody say, 'Amen.'And we call healing for your bodies and for your finances.

00:30:45.507 --> 00:30:51.087
Sorry, I always want to pray for that, so you're healed and whole and well.

00:30:51.088 --> 00:30:55.250
And we thank You, Lord, for everyone that is suffering from sickness and disease.

00:30:55.251 --> 00:30:59.887
We pray blessing and healing power over their bodies right now in the name of Jesus.

00:30:59.888 --> 00:31:05.301
We take authority over sickness and disease, and we thank You, Lord, that You've delivered them from this.

00:31:05.302 --> 00:31:08.843
You've already done it, and we receive what You've done by faith.

00:31:08.844 --> 00:31:14.660
And we speak to those things, and we call those things that be not as though they were over their lives in Jesus'name.

00:31:14.661 --> 00:31:20.604
And we give You all the glory and all the praise for what You've already done, Lord, in Jesus'name.

00:31:20.605 --> 00:31:25.099
All right, y'all, put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:31:25.100 --> 00:31:39.294
Jesus loves you so much, and we love you so much, you all. And we thank you for being a part of our little community here. God bless you guys, and we'll see you next time. Bye-bye.

